    "This work aims to provide a comprehensive overview of the landscape of LMFMs in education, with a specific focus on the latest advancements represented by LMFMs, thereby contributing to the ongoing dialogue on the role of AI in shaping the future of education.",
    "Opportunities for LearnersPersonalized learning assistants can have multiple benefits for learners.",
